title: IAA Tonight | Terrell Owens Makes a Surprise Visit to IAA Tonight
description: Brandon Marshall, Adam Pacman Jones and Leger Douzable get a surprise visit from none other than Hall of Fame WR Terrell Owens after he calls out Brandon to race him in a 40 yard dash. Plus, Pacmans Bengals got into a heated fight with the Rams today in which Aaron Donald was swinging helmets at Rams players.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Brandon Marshall, Adam Pacman Jones, Leger Douzable, Terrell Owens)
